commit.message: Fix installation on OCaml builds without shared library support.
Ignore and clean an oUnit temporary file.
Add a file required by tests.
Make bytecode tests runnable without installation.
Fix the Makefile to be independent of OS-specific file extensions.

Add cross-compilation support, using ocamlfind -toolchain.

ocamlfind now provides an easy way to cross-compile; the only thing
needed to use it is to compile all code (both OCaml and C) through
ocamlfind.
Remove a copy of the entire archive accidentally nested in.
